  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Of course, Elsa, mom!",
      "zh": "當然了，艾莎，媽媽！",
      "ja": "もちろん、エルサ、ママ！",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And thus we lived in the place of happily ever after.",
      "zh": "於是我們就這樣幸福快樂地生活著。",
      "ja": "そして私たちはいつまでも幸せに暮らしました。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One whole day!",
      "zh": "整整一天！",
      "ja": "丸一日！",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop it, Sven! That tickles out!",
      "zh": "停下，斯文！那會癢啦！",
      "ja": "やめて、スヴェン！くすぐったいよ！",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, hey, ouch! Ouch!",
      "zh": "嘿，嘿，哎呀！哎呀！",
      "ja": "おいおい、痛い！痛い！",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love baby hedgehogs.",
      "zh": "我喜歡小刺蝟。",
      "ja": "赤ちゃんハリネズミが大好き。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Gotta touch that belly.",
      "zh": "一定要摸那個肚子。",
      "ja": "あの腹を触らなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ow! Oh, ah, ah, ah! I still love them.",
      "zh": "哎呦！喔，啊，啊，啊！我還是愛牠們。",
      "ja": "痛っ！ああ、ああ、ああ！それでも好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is it so hot in here?",
      "zh": "這裡怎麼這麼熱？",
      "ja": "なんでここはこんなに暑いの？",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah! I want to touch the belly!",
      "zh": "啊！我想摸肚子！",
      "ja": "ああ！腹を触りたい！",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You two, I woke up with a swirl in my bed.",
      "zh": "你們兩個，我醒來時床上全是旋渦。",
      "ja": "君たち二人、ベッドがぐちゃぐちゃで目が覚めたよ。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your bed? My head.",
      "zh": "你的床？我的頭。",
      "ja": "君のベッド？僕の頭だ。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey, guys!",
      "zh": "喔，嘿，大家！",
      "ja": "ああ、やあ、みんな！",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's going on?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is it not obvious? Let me explain it to you.",
      "zh": "還不明顯嗎？讓我來解釋給你們聽。",
      "ja": "わからないの？説明しよう。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "When Elsa leaves her deadly eternal winter in the middle of summer,",
      "zh": "當艾莎在夏天中間帶來致命的永恆冬季，",
      "ja": "エルサが夏の真ん中に致命的な永遠の冬をもたらすと、",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "she upset the natural balance of the surrounding forest,",
      "zh": "她打亂了周圍森林的自然平衡，",
      "ja": "彼女は周囲の森の自然のバランスを崩してしまう。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "thus creating a severe threat of starvation,",
      "zh": "因此造成嚴重的飢餓威脅，",
      "ja": "それにより深刻な飢餓の脅威を生み出す。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "loss of safe shelter, panic,",
      "zh": "失去安全的庇護，恐慌，",
      "ja": "安全な避難所の喪失、パニック、",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and a pervasive fight-flight or freeze response.",
      "zh": "以及普遍的戰鬥、逃跑或凍結反應。",
      "ja": "そして広範囲にわたる闘争・逃走・凍結反応。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But why are they all baby animals?",
      "zh": "但為什麼都是小動物？",
      "ja": "でも、なぜみんな赤ちゃん動物なの？",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please, Kristoff, raise your hand before asking questions.",
      "zh": "請克里斯托夫，問問題前先舉手。",
      "ja": "クリストフ、質問する前に手を挙げてください。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See, that's the true tragedy of Elsa's knowing tantrum.",
      "zh": "看，那就是艾莎故意發脾氣的真正悲劇。",
      "ja": "それがエルサのわざとらしい癇癪の本当の悲劇だ。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Parents and desperate search for food will force to leave their young ones",
      "zh": "父母為了絕望地尋找食物，會被迫離開幼崽，",
      "ja": "親は必死に食べ物を探すために幼い子を置き去りにせざるを得ない。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "to fend the brutal elements alone.",
      "zh": "讓他們獨自面對嚴酷的環境。",
      "ja": "過酷な自然環境に一人で立ち向かわせるのだ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then it's my fault.",
      "zh": "那就是我的錯。",
      "ja": "それなら僕のせいだ。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You said it, got me.",
      "zh": "你說對了，我認了。",
      "ja": "その通りだ、認めるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do we do?",
      "zh": "我們該怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "どうすればいい？",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, they can stay with us here in the castle",
      "zh": "嗯，他們可以留在城堡裡和我們一起，",
      "ja": "そうだな、ここ城で私たちと一緒にいればいい。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "until their parents get back.",
      "zh": "直到他們的父母回來。",
      "ja": "親が戻るまでの間。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-oh.",
      "zh": "糟了。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If they stay here, there won't be any castle.",
      "zh": "如果他們留在這裡，就不會有城堡了。",
      "ja": "ここにいれば城はなくなるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How about we take them to my fishing fortress on the fjord?",
      "zh": "我們帶他們去我在峽灣的釣魚堡壘怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "私のフィヨルドの釣り要塞に連れて行こうか？",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's amazing. And private.",
      "zh": "那裡很棒，而且很隱密。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいし、プライベートだ。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "あっ！",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I built it myself.",
      "zh": "是我自己建的。",
      "ja": "自分で建てたんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There she is.",
      "zh": "它就在那裡。",
      "ja": "あそこにある。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at her.",
      "zh": "看看它。",
      "ja": "見てごらん。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a bit of a fixer-upper.",
      "zh": "有點需要修繕。",
      "ja": "ちょっと手直しが必要だ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You like what I did there?",
      "zh": "你喜歡我做的嗎？",
      "ja": "気に入ったかい？",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can work with it.",
      "zh": "我可以接受。",
      "ja": "なんとかなるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ah, look.",
      "zh": "啊，看。",
      "ja": "ああ、見て。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sven, you go find their parents while we pretend we know what we're doing here.",
      "zh": "斯文，你去找他們的父母，我們這邊假裝知道自己在做什麼。",
      "ja": "スヴェン、君は親を探しに行って、私たちはここで何をしているか知っているふりをしよう。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But we don't know the first thing about caring for baby animals.",
      "zh": "但我們一點也不懂怎麼照顧小動物。",
      "ja": "でも赤ちゃん動物の世話なんて全然わからないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Our families looked after an entire kingdom for generations.",
      "zh": "我們的家族世代照顧整個王國。",
      "ja": "私たちの家族は何世代にもわたり王国を守ってきた。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And Elsa almost killed them in one day.",
      "zh": "而艾莎差點一天就毀了它們。",
      "ja": "そしてエルサは一日でそれをほぼ壊してしまった。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What could possibly go wrong?",
      "zh": "會有什麼可能出錯呢？",
      "ja": "何がうまくいかないっていうんだ？",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "zh": "喔，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いやだ。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Elsa!",
      "zh": "艾莎！",
      "ja": "エルサ！",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, whoa!",
      "zh": "嘿，哇！",
      "ja": "おい、わっ！",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, boy.",
      "zh": "喔，天啊。",
      "ja": "ああ、こりゃ。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Rapids poop nonstop!",
      "zh": "急流不停地拉屎！",
      "ja": "急流は止まらずにうんちをする！",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The smell!",
      "zh": "味道！",
      "ja": "臭い！",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, the smell!",
      "zh": "喔，味道！",
      "ja": "ああ、臭い！",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So cute, so painful?",
      "zh": "好可愛，好痛苦？",
      "ja": "かわいいけど、つらい？",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's not done.",
      "zh": "還沒結束。",
      "ja": "まだ終わってない。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, what are you getting?",
      "zh": "是啊，你要拿什麼？",
      "ja": "そうだ、何を取るんだ？",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You don't get upset.",
      "zh": "你不要生氣。",
      "ja": "怒らないで。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You want for you?",
      "zh": "你想要給你？",
      "ja": "君のために？",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You.",
      "zh": "你。",
      "ja": "君。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Consider them pacified.",
      "zh": "算是安撫好了。",
      "ja": "落ち着いたと思おう。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "おお！",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh!",
      "zh": "噓！",
      "ja": "しーっ！",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh!",
      "zh": "噓！",
      "ja": "しーっ！",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh!",
      "zh": "噓！",
      "ja": "しーっ！",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We did it!",
      "zh": "我們成功了！",
      "ja": "やった！",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are all children this exhausting?",
      "zh": "所有小孩都這麼累人嗎？",
      "ja": "子供ってみんなこんなに疲れるの？",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Spin!",
      "zh": "旋轉！",
      "ja": "スピン！",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye!",
      "zh": "再見！",
      "ja": "バイバイ！",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye!",
      "zh": "再見！",
      "ja": "バイバイ！",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "zh": "不好意思。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Elsa said sorry about the Holy Turtle winter thing.",
      "zh": "艾莎說對神聖烏龜冬季的事感到抱歉。",
      "ja": "エルサはホーリータートルの冬のことを謝っていたよ。",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We did it.",
      "zh": "我們做到了。",
      "ja": "やり遂げた。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That wasn't so hard.",
      "zh": "那並不難。",
      "ja": "そんなに難しくなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our shelter smells like musk ox.",
      "zh": "我們的庇護所聞起來像麝香牛。",
      "ja": "私たちの避難所はジャコウウシの匂いがする。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's an impermanent.",
      "zh": "這是暫時的。",
      "ja": "それは一時的なものだ。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And that's now we live in a peaceful, happily ever after.",
      "zh": "這就是我們現在和平幸福地生活著。",
      "ja": "そして今、私たちは平和に幸せに暮らしている。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Assuming Elsa doesn't cure voices in her sleep calling to her through song.",
      "zh": "當然前提是艾莎不會在睡夢中被歌聲呼喚而醒來。",
      "ja": "エルサが眠っている間に歌声に呼ばれて目覚めない限りね。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    }
  ]
}